profile:
Steele Pools is based out of Oakville, ON.  We service Oakville, Burlington, Mississauga, Ancaster, Hamilton and Toronto.  We create custom swimming pools, water features, high end natural stonework, beautiful flagstone patios, outdoor kitchens, and more.   
We pride ourselves on using the highest quality products available and attention to even the smallest details in our workmanship.  
We specialize in Custom swimming pools and natural stonework.
We believe in quality over quantity and building a fantasy backyard oasis to last you and your family years to come.
